00:20:03,827 --> 00:20:06,955
No, I got an A in this class
in my first year.

259
00:20:07,539 --> 00:20:09,041
Oh, I see.

260
00:20:10,459 --> 00:20:12,044
Then what are you doing here?

261
00:20:12,127 --> 00:20:14,546
What do you think? I came to see you.

262
00:20:16,673 --> 00:20:18,383
What on earth is he doing here?

263
00:20:18,467 --> 00:20:20,177
Does he have to retake this class?

264
00:20:20,260 --> 00:20:22,804
It looks like
he's trying to hit on Mi-rae.

265
00:20:23,388 --> 00:20:27,476
Right, when Mi-rae walked in earlier,
I could see how much she stands out.

266
00:20:27,809 --> 00:20:28,644
Really?

267
00:20:30,229 --> 00:20:32,314
But as soon as Sua walked in...

268
00:20:32,773 --> 00:20:34,942
What? Did you call me?

269
00:20:35,400 --> 00:20:37,361
No, no. I didn't call you.

270
00:20:38,445 --> 00:20:40,614
I'm such an idiot.

271
00:20:40,697 --> 00:20:44,368
I wanted to call you but I realized
that I never asked your number.

272
00:20:46,495 --> 00:20:47,663
I see.

273
00:20:47,746 --> 00:20:50,332
What's up?
Did the entrance ceremony go well?

274
00:20:51,541 --> 00:20:52,376
Yes.

275
00:20:52,459 --> 00:20:55,587
If there's anything you don't understand,
feel free to ask me.

276
00:20:55,671 --> 00:20:57,589
I got an A in General Chemistry.

277
00:20:58,840 --> 00:21:02,219
Also, I have all the exam notes
for this class.

278
00:21:02,302 --> 00:21:04,554
This professor's exams are the same
every year.

279
00:21:04,638 --> 00:21:06,640
Do you know what I mean by "exam notes"?

280
00:21:06,723 --> 00:21:10,269
It seems like you can only see Mi-rae.
We'll need them, too.

281
00:21:10,352 --> 00:21:13,981
Figure it our yourself.
Mi-rae and I have a special relationship.

282
00:21:14,856 --> 00:21:15,691
Me?

283
00:21:15,774 --> 00:21:17,651
We did couple drinking.
Didn't we?

284
00:21:21,071 --> 00:21:24,116
Oh, shall we have lunch together
at the cafeteria?

285
00:21:24,199 --> 00:21:25,284
Sorry?

286
00:21:25,367 --> 00:21:28,412
Today's menu looks amazing.
Girls, you'd better not come.

287
00:21:37,587 --> 00:21:39,047
Mi-rae, let's sit over there.

288
00:21:52,519 --> 00:21:54,646
This is on me, so eat everything you want.

289
00:21:55,564 --> 00:21:56,440
Thank you.

290
00:22:01,236 --> 00:22:03,739
How is it?
The food at our cafeteria is quite good.

291
00:22:04,239 --> 00:22:06,241
-Yes, it's good.
-Good.

292
00:22:16,293 --> 00:22:17,419
You know...

293
00:22:19,171 --> 00:22:21,131
I asked you if I can like you.

294
00:22:22,299 --> 00:22:24,509
I think you've had enough time to ponder.

295
00:22:26,511 --> 00:22:28,930
Should we not talk about it at school?

296
00:22:29,014 --> 00:22:31,850
Shall we go to a nice bar in the evening?

297
00:22:34,436 --> 00:22:36,980
-Do you want some water?
-No, it's okay.

298
00:22:37,064 --> 00:22:39,191
-I'll use the restroom quickly.
-All right.

299
00:22:42,402 --> 00:22:44,780
Gosh, why is she acting all naive?

300
00:22:49,659 --> 00:22:51,078
Hello, Chan-woo.

301
00:22:51,661 --> 00:22:52,662
Sua.

302
00:22:54,790 --> 00:22:58,585
You're in the same General Chemistry class
with us, right?

303
00:22:59,503 --> 00:23:03,173
Oh, I'm not actually in the class.
I just stopped by to see you guys.

304
00:23:03,256 --> 00:23:07,636
I was wondering
why you were retaking a first-year course.

305
00:23:08,261 --> 00:23:09,805
Oh, were you curious?

306
00:23:11,348 --> 00:23:13,517
-Have a seat. We can chat.
-Sure.

307
00:23:17,229 --> 00:23:21,274
Isn't somebody else sitting here?

308
00:23:21,358 --> 00:23:24,361
-It's Mi-rae. She went to the restroom.
-I see.

309
00:23:26,363 --> 00:23:29,366
Chan-woo, you like Mi-rae, don't you?

310
00:23:29,449 --> 00:23:34,454
Well, I think all of you are adorable.
That includes you.

311
00:23:34,579 --> 00:23:37,874
Just talk casually to me.
You don't need to be so polite.

312
00:23:39,376 --> 00:23:43,213
I think you and Mi-rae
will make a cute couple.

313
00:23:44,756 --> 00:23:47,008
Well, we're not there yet.

314
00:23:48,510 --> 00:23:50,137
I'll be cheering for you.

315
00:23:51,430 --> 00:23:52,931
Although I'm a little sad.

316
00:23:54,433 --> 00:23:55,308
What do you mean?

317
00:23:57,102 --> 00:24:00,105
Nothing. Never mind.
I should get going now.

318
00:24:00,313 --> 00:24:01,481
Hey, wait.

319
00:24:02,482 --> 00:24:05,360
What did you mean by that?
Why are you sad?

320
00:24:05,444 --> 00:24:06,611
Well...

321
00:24:06,736 --> 00:24:08,029
Oh, sorry.

322
00:24:12,325 --> 00:24:13,577
I can sit here, right?

323
00:24:14,703 --> 00:24:18,373
Hey, how could you ignore
all of my messages for three days?

324
00:24:18,748 --> 00:24:20,000
I guess you've been busy.

325
00:24:20,083 --> 00:24:21,543
I don't check my phone often.

326
00:24:21,668 --> 00:24:24,337
Goodness,
that's why you don't have a girlfriend.

327
00:24:25,630 --> 00:24:26,506
Come on, tell me.

328
00:24:27,549 --> 00:24:29,217
To tell you the truth,

329
00:24:29,885 --> 00:24:34,306
I was quite smitten by you
at the freshmen orientation.

330
00:24:35,223 --> 00:24:36,433
What? Me?

331
00:24:37,100 --> 00:24:39,186
Don't take it too seriously though.

332
00:24:39,269 --> 00:24:42,939
I'm over you now,
so you don't need to care too much. Okay?

333
00:24:43,398 --> 00:24:44,483
No, wait.

334
00:24:52,240 --> 00:24:53,200
Gosh.

335
00:24:54,159 --> 00:24:55,202
I can't believe...

336
00:24:59,873 --> 00:25:01,041
I'm sorry.

337
00:25:02,042 --> 00:25:04,836
I just want to think of you as my senior.

338
00:25:09,216 --> 00:25:11,885
I just want to think of you as my senior.

339
00:25:13,053 --> 00:25:16,223
I just want to think of you
as my senior...

340
00:25:21,019 --> 00:25:23,271
-Chan-woo.
-Hey, Mi-rae.

341
00:25:23,355 --> 00:25:25,565
Let's just be friends. Okay?

342
00:25:26,483 --> 00:25:27,400
Pardon?

343
00:25:27,484 --> 00:25:30,946
What I said to you was a mistake.

344
00:25:31,696 --> 00:25:35,325
I think I was confused.
I actually like someone else.

345
00:25:35,408 --> 00:25:37,369
I'm sorry for making things complicated.

346
00:25:37,827 --> 00:25:40,455
I'm sorry.
You understand what I'm saying, right?

347
00:25:40,705 --> 00:25:44,000
I'm sorry if you took it seriously.
Is everything okay?

348
00:25:44,084 --> 00:25:45,627
You can finish your meal.

349
00:26:01,685 --> 00:26:03,853
Sorry, my mistake.

350
00:26:05,021 --> 00:26:06,856
Is it you again, you jerk?

351
00:26:09,734 --> 00:26:11,152
What did you just say?

352
00:26:11,736 --> 00:26:12,779
"Mistake"?

353
00:26:14,614 --> 00:26:15,574
Do you want to die?

354
00:26:16,449 --> 00:26:18,451
Huh? My gosh.

355
00:26:19,953 --> 00:26:21,288
This is a mistake as well.

356
00:26:26,209 --> 00:26:27,294
You must want to die.

357
00:26:29,337 --> 00:26:30,213
I'm done eating.

358
00:26:30,755 --> 00:26:33,258
You must be crazy for a beating. Hey!

359
00:26:38,179 --> 00:26:40,181
-What's wrong with him?
-My gosh.

360
00:26:41,975 --> 00:26:44,561
You little jerk.
I'm going to kill you.

361
00:26:47,689 --> 00:26:49,774
-Chan-woo.
-What are you doing?

362
00:26:49,858 --> 00:26:51,860
Are you taking his side? Move!

363
00:27:20,597 --> 00:27:22,432
Chan-woo, what are you doing?

364
00:27:22,515 --> 00:27:24,851
-Let go of me!
-Everyone's staring.

365
00:27:24,934 --> 00:27:28,104
-What's his problem?
-My gosh.

366
00:27:28,188 --> 00:27:31,483
-Why is he always causing trouble?
-Let me go.

367
00:27:32,067 --> 00:27:33,943
You better consider yourself lucky.

368
00:27:34,027 --> 00:27:36,404
I'm going to kill you
the next time I see you. Okay?

369
00:27:37,530 --> 00:27:39,407
Why is he always causing trouble?

370
00:27:39,866 --> 00:27:42,410
What a joke. Isn't he the jerk
from chemistry?

371
00:27:42,494 --> 00:27:44,621
-What was that?
-Oh, gosh.

372
00:27:45,163 --> 00:27:46,206
Are you okay?

373
00:27:55,548 --> 00:27:58,343
My gosh. I'm sorry.

374
00:28:17,278 --> 00:28:19,239
They were fighting like crazy.

375
00:28:20,782 --> 00:28:22,784
Do you know what Chan-woo's nickname is?

376
00:28:25,078 --> 00:28:27,497
It's SOJ. It stands for son of a jerk.

377
00:28:30,583 --> 00:28:32,585
You need to be careful of guys like him.

378
00:28:32,919 --> 00:28:35,797
Sua, you better watch out as well.

379
00:28:36,840 --> 00:28:37,757
Okay.

380
00:28:40,635 --> 00:28:41,970
What? Oh, okay.

381
00:28:43,263 --> 00:28:44,681
Oh, well...

382
00:28:44,889 --> 00:28:47,809
What do you think about having chicken
and beer after class?

383
00:28:48,309 --> 00:28:49,436
Are you up for it?

384
00:28:52,063 --> 00:28:56,317
Well, I'm up for it if Sua is.

385
00:28:58,236 --> 00:28:59,654
My gosh.

386
00:29:06,161 --> 00:29:08,246
Sorry, my mistake.

387
00:29:10,373 --> 00:29:11,624
How cute.

388
00:29:16,129 --> 00:29:16,963
What?

389
00:29:17,046 --> 00:29:20,300
She thinks you're cute.

390
00:29:22,719 --> 00:29:25,263
Sua, there you are.

391
00:29:26,181 --> 00:29:28,057
-Hello.
-Hi.

392
00:29:29,058 --> 00:29:31,811
Can we talk outside in private?

393
00:29:33,104 --> 00:29:33,938
Sure.

394
00:29:34,606 --> 00:29:35,982
I'll wait for you outside.

395
00:29:46,659 --> 00:29:50,121
What I'm about to tell you comes from
the bottom of my heart.

396
00:29:50,205 --> 00:29:51,498
So please hear me out.

397
00:29:53,082 --> 00:29:54,542
-Okay.
-Right.

398
00:29:54,918 --> 00:30:00,173
Guys always have their own ideal type
of girl in mind.

399
00:30:00,757 --> 00:30:01,883
The same goes for me.

400
00:30:01,966 --> 00:30:05,970
When I first saw you,
my heart almost dropped to the ground.

401
00:30:06,387 --> 00:30:09,557
I'll be straightforward with you.
You're my ideal type of girl.

402
00:30:10,433 --> 00:30:14,687
You're the only one I was interested in
ever since the freshmen welcoming party.

403
00:30:15,355 --> 00:30:16,856
You might not believe me,

404
00:30:18,483 --> 00:30:21,778
but I tend to get really shy
around the person I like.

405
00:30:21,861 --> 00:30:26,282
But now that
I know you feel the same way about me,

406
00:30:26,366 --> 00:30:29,577
I was wondering
if you'd like to start going out with me.

407
00:30:29,661 --> 00:30:32,455
Then what about Mi-rae?

408
00:30:33,623 --> 00:30:35,959
I was nice to her
because she was in my team,

409
00:30:36,042 --> 00:30:38,169
and she did good in the talent show.

410
00:30:38,253 --> 00:30:40,046
You were the only girl I liked.

411
00:30:42,465 --> 00:30:43,466
Sua.

412
00:30:46,553 --> 00:30:50,348
I'm really grateful
that you think of me that way.

413
00:30:50,557 --> 00:30:51,391
Okay.

414
00:30:51,683 --> 00:30:54,310
But can you give me some time
to think about it?

415
00:30:55,436 --> 00:30:57,605
Yes, of course. You should think about it.

416
00:30:57,689 --> 00:31:00,817
Although it won't be a problem
since we both like each other.

417
00:31:00,900 --> 00:31:03,403
Anyway, well...

418
00:31:04,153 --> 00:31:07,323
I'll wait for your call.

419
00:31:09,450 --> 00:31:10,368
Bye.

420
00:31:15,498 --> 00:31:16,416
Sua.

421
00:31:20,253 --> 00:31:21,254
Did anything happen?

422
00:31:21,838 --> 00:31:23,756
What? What do you mean?

423
00:31:24,632 --> 00:31:27,218
Is Chan-woo hitting on you?

424
00:31:28,595 --> 00:31:29,762
No.

425
00:31:30,597 --> 00:31:33,182
He just said
what all the other seniors said to me.

426
00:31:33,349 --> 00:31:35,977
He told me to let him know
if I need any help.

427
00:31:36,686 --> 00:31:40,773
Who else said that to you?
Jung-hwan? Jin-wook?

428
00:31:46,237 --> 00:31:48,448
I can't believe he made a fool out of me.

429
00:31:49,365 --> 00:31:51,826
Do I still seem like a joke to everyone?

430
00:31:53,119 --> 00:31:57,040
Remember when I asked you
if it'd be okay for me to like you?

431
00:31:57,123 --> 00:31:59,459
-Chan-woo.
-Hey, Mi-rae.

432
00:31:59,542 --> 00:32:02,462
What I said to you was a mistake.

433
00:32:03,671 --> 00:32:07,425
I think I was confused.
I actually like someone else.

434
00:32:35,203 --> 00:32:36,037
Are you okay?

435
00:32:44,253 --> 00:32:45,129
Are you okay?

436
00:32:48,341 --> 00:32:50,551
I was looking for you
because I was worried.

437
00:32:51,386 --> 00:32:54,764
I heard Chan-woo and Kyung-seok
had a fight at the cafeteria.

438
00:32:55,974 --> 00:32:58,643
I heard Chan-woo even pushed you.

439
00:32:59,978 --> 00:33:01,396
Did you get hurt?

440
00:33:02,855 --> 00:33:03,982
No.

441
00:33:05,483 --> 00:33:06,776
What happened?

442
00:33:07,735 --> 00:33:10,738
I thought things were going well
between you and Chan-woo.

443
00:33:15,118 --> 00:33:16,619
What's going on?

444
00:33:17,787 --> 00:33:18,871
I don't know.

445
00:33:19,539 --> 00:33:22,208
He asked me to go out,
but then said it was a mistake.

446
00:33:23,042 --> 00:33:26,879
Is that why Kyung-seok got mad
and fought with him?

447
00:33:27,505 --> 00:33:31,050
No, they fought
because Kyung-seok made Chan-woo trip.

448
00:33:32,010 --> 00:33:33,261
I see.

449
00:33:35,847 --> 00:33:36,848
Do you...

450
00:33:38,725 --> 00:33:40,685
have a crush on Chan-woo?

451
00:33:41,269 --> 00:33:42,145
No.

452
00:33:44,105 --> 00:33:45,273
Not at all.

453
00:33:45,356 --> 00:33:48,484
I'm so relieved that
he doesn't actually have feelings for me.

454
00:33:48,609 --> 00:33:51,654
Yes, don't let it bother you.

455
00:33:52,238 --> 00:33:56,993
Have you heard?
Chan-woo's nickname is SOJ. Son of Jerk.

456
00:33:57,076 --> 00:34:00,788
He should behave himself as a senior.
Why does he have to bother freshmen?

457
00:34:00,872 --> 00:34:02,623
He's so annoying.

458
00:34:06,794 --> 00:34:09,047
Just forget about it.
Don't take it to heart.

459
00:34:09,255 --> 00:34:10,465
You have me, you know.

460
00:34:11,215 --> 00:34:13,926
I have you?

461
00:34:14,510 --> 00:34:16,429
We'll be late for our class. Let's go.

462
00:34:18,097 --> 00:34:19,223
Okay.

463
00:34:20,933 --> 00:34:24,103
If he bothers my friend again,
I'll teach him a serious lesson.

464
00:34:24,187 --> 00:34:25,813
"My friend"?

465
00:34:25,938 --> 00:34:28,274
Friends must help each other.
Aren't I right?

466
00:34:29,108 --> 00:34:31,152
Yes, thanks.

467
00:34:31,903 --> 00:34:35,990
You just smiled. Do you feel better now?

468
00:34:39,535 --> 00:34:40,912
She's an angel.

469
00:34:42,830 --> 00:34:45,458
Yes, I'm totally fine now.

470
00:34:47,210 --> 00:34:50,797
Hello, I'm Yeon Woo-young.
I'll be helping you with your experiments.

471
00:34:55,760 --> 00:34:58,763
First, I'll explain
how the experiments will work.

472
00:34:58,846 --> 00:35:00,890
After that, you'll split up into teams.

473
00:35:02,141 --> 00:35:04,811
-We're sorry.
-We're sorry.

474
00:35:06,521 --> 00:35:11,651
