Each team will consist of 5 to 6 students.

475
00:35:11,734 --> 00:35:14,654
You'll be graded as teams,
so please help each other out.

476
00:35:15,446 --> 00:35:18,282
Let's split you into teams.
We'll do a random draw.

477
00:35:18,908 --> 00:35:21,911
I can't believe we have to do
team experiments in this class.

478
00:35:21,994 --> 00:35:25,414
Gosh, I really hope I can team up
with someone I know.

479
00:35:25,498 --> 00:35:27,500
-I heard this is hard.
-Somebody I know.

480
00:35:28,209 --> 00:35:31,129
Someone I know, please.

481
00:35:33,422 --> 00:35:34,298
Team 3

482
00:35:36,884 --> 00:35:38,511
Mi-rae, are you in Team One?

483
00:35:39,095 --> 00:35:40,346
No, Team Three.

484
00:35:40,888 --> 00:35:42,473
Won-ho, are you in Team Three?

485
00:35:42,598 --> 00:35:45,643
I was worried. Thank goodness
one teammate is someone I know.

486
00:35:45,726 --> 00:35:47,895
Gosh, you idiot.

487
00:35:49,272 --> 00:35:51,649
I hope there's a pretty girl in our team.

488
00:35:53,442 --> 00:35:55,903
Hey, Won-ho. Are both of you in this team?

489
00:35:56,487 --> 00:35:58,656
-What are you doing here?
-What?

490
00:35:58,739 --> 00:36:01,576
I was hoping a pretty girl would join us.
Why you?

491
00:36:01,659 --> 00:36:03,578
-Are you dumb?
-Whatever, Ji-hyo.

492
00:36:03,661 --> 00:36:07,373
You're the type to go off the grid
when we have a group assignment.

493
00:36:07,456 --> 00:36:08,875
Shall I teach you a lesson?

494
00:36:08,958 --> 00:36:10,084
I want to live.

495
00:36:12,086 --> 00:36:15,548
I bet Won-ho will enlist in the army
after getting dumped by a girl.

496
00:36:16,507 --> 00:36:19,719
You'll be a total outcast
when you join the military, you idiot.

497
00:36:19,802 --> 00:36:21,721
-Totally.
-Okay.

498
00:36:23,514 --> 00:36:24,849
Are you in Team Three too?

499
00:36:25,391 --> 00:36:26,767
-Yes.
-Me too.

500
00:36:27,560 --> 00:36:29,020
We're in the same team, then.

501
00:36:29,103 --> 00:36:30,271
-Really?
-Yes.

502
00:36:32,648 --> 00:36:35,568
Is Sua the last one to join our team?

503
00:36:35,693 --> 00:36:36,694
Is this Team Three?

504
00:36:40,656 --> 00:36:44,952
This is amazing. All the celebrities
of the first year are in our team.

505
00:36:45,536 --> 00:36:46,704
-"Celebrities"?
-Yes.

506
00:36:46,787 --> 00:36:49,081
You and Kyung-seok are very famous.

507
00:36:51,083 --> 00:36:52,627
So is Mi-rae.

508
00:36:56,547 --> 00:36:59,091
Each team leader
needs to guide the team members

509
00:36:59,175 --> 00:37:00,927
and make sure to submit the reports.

510
00:37:01,969 --> 00:37:04,180
What should we do?
